OL,3,CFormer Christian Brother handed 10-
OL,4,Cyear sentence for historic child abuse
OL,6,FA former teacher and school principal
OL,7,Fconvicted of historical child sex
OL,8,Fabuse has been handed a further 10
OL,9,Fyears in prison.
OL,11,FFormer Christian Brother Paul
OL,12,FDunleavy, 89, with an address in Glen
OL,13,FRoad, Belfast, was found guilty in
OL,14,FSeptember of 36 charges of historical
OL,15,Fsexual abuse against nine boys.
OL,17,FThe charges included indecent assault
OL,18,Fand gross indecency with or towards a
OL,19,Fchild.
